HEADWORD: Dentation
<hw>Den*ta"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Formation of
teeth; toothed form.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>How did it [a bill] get its barb, its <qex>dentation</qex>?</q>
